name: Cave Painting (24/10/2021 SEASONS)
description: An artwork in the Cave Painting Series by the artist M Plummer-Fernández. Created 22/10/2021 and minted 24/10/2021. The prompts Spring, Summer, Autumn, Winter defined the transformations in this work. The Cave Paintings are produced by a custom neural network system that imagines caves in response to prompts chosen by the artist.
